<p>The rosy glasses are interesting but it is kind of like a regular anomalous object, the object just gives a rush of dopamine but it is just a pair of magical glasses that makes the wearer happy and doesn't really warrant an article, just contained on one of the security lockers with the key being held by a researcher and having an entry in the list of anomalous objects</p>
