<p>Here it is:<br />
<a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/doggols-sandbox-ii">http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/doggols-sandbox-ii</a></p>
<p>Under the tab 'Criticism and Review:**</p>
<p>My concerns:</p>
<ul>
<li>Weirdness - Is it too hard to understand, can the mystery be solved?</li>
<li>Length - Is it too long or too short?</li>
<li>Story - Is the story behind it good enough?</li>
<li>Consistency - Is the anomaly consistent?</li>
