<p><strong>Seeking Greenlights:</strong> Yes</p>
<p><strong>Page Type:</strong> SCP Article</p>
<p><strong>Genre (Optional):</strong> Horror, Other: Discovery</p>
<p><strong>Page Layout (Optional):</strong> The page will have some test logs, addendums and audio logs</p>
<p><strong>Elevator Pitch:</strong> In Antarctica a dark portal to another dimension suddenly appears, after some scientists get lost in Antarctica the foundation started an investigation. That is when they found the dark warriors. Lead by a general corrupted by darkness.</p>
<p><strong>Central Narrative:</strong> After the foundation finds the portal and the creatures a provisional site is built around the portal. The SCP includes two entities, the general and his soldiers (proxies). The general commands his proxies or the proxies act on their own attacking any life-forms not &quot;Embracing the dark&quot;. The general and his proxies are dark they don't have: skin, skeletons or even organs. the general is rarely seen his soldiers are mostly in our dimension and not in the &quot;Dark&quot; dimension. Both the soldiers and the general can corrupt biological life forms by killing them, when a human is killed a dark goo consumes them and turns them into a soldier but if the body is too damaged or did not die by the hands of the entities no transformation will happen. All dark entities have a severe case of Photophobia<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-774249-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-774249-1')">1</a></sup> since light can hurt and melt them. Inside the portal there seems to be a world which had a SK-Class Dominance Shift Scenario where the entities took over earth in that dimension but humans still survived and are near extinction. The foundation also found the general is building an army which could result in a BI Class Pre-Invasion Scenario.</p>
