<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>Hook/Attention-Grabber:</strong> The attention grabber here is the army. It's goals are yet unknown and it's size is large and feared. I think readers would want to continue reading to know the mysterious outcome of the article.</p>
<p><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> None</p>
