<p>Hi everybody, my names Phil and I'm just here chasing my joy.</p>
<p>I'm a recent University graduate who after some self evaluating recognized that the aspect of my degree I enjoyed most was the storytelling. I've always been a fan of the SCP universe and the way its many stories are spun together into an ever expanding universe of many minds. So I thought, where better to practice writing than here?</p>
<p>I'm a massive fan of collaborative story telling, a result of my immersion in ttrpg culture and nerdom, and really wanted the experience of discussing narrative with a community. This will be some of my first writing uploaded to a large public space and I find myself both excited and nervous to take the plunge. Thanks so much for anytime you might've spent on my ramblings and I hope to talk to and share my work with people soon. :)</p>

